# Web3Forms access key for the contact form.
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com and enter the inbox email that should receive
#    inquiries — you'll get an access key by email instantly (free, no signup).
# 2. Copy this file to ".env" and paste your key below.
# 3. Restart `npm run dev` so Vite picks up the new value.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=your-access-key-here
